<field name="name">

&lt;P&gt;
chdir - change your current working directory

&lt;P&gt;
&lt;HR&gt;
</field>
<field name="synopsis">

&lt;P&gt;
chdir 
&lt;FONT SIZE=-1&gt;EXPR&lt;/FONT&gt;

&lt;P&gt;
&lt;HR&gt;
</field>
<field name="description">

&lt;P&gt;
Changes the working directory to 
&lt;FONT SIZE=-1&gt;EXPR,&lt;/FONT&gt; if possible. If 
&lt;FONT SIZE=-1&gt;EXPR&lt;/FONT&gt; is omitted, changes to home directory. Returns 
&lt;FONT SIZE=-1&gt;TRUE&lt;/FONT&gt; upon success, 
&lt;FONT SIZE=-1&gt;FALSE&lt;/FONT&gt; otherwise. See example under
 [perlfunc:die|die()].

&lt;HR&gt;
</field>
